#Srcthl
	srcthl is tools to format the src code to html format document.

#Support platform
	Windows NT , Linux, Freebsd...,Some Posix Systems are also support 
	(see src/build.h Macro for this platform).

#Build
	Windows NT : Windows.mak using nmake tools.
	Linux      : Linux.mak using gmake tools.
	Freebsd    : Freebsd.mak using gmake tools.

Execpt the Windows NT, the other system is also use the gmake(gnu make) tools.


#Development
	The src directory is the src code.
	The doc directory is the doc.
	README for readme.
